<sect1 id="dir_2e322012c304bd84ecea0543a8b62f92_1autotoc_md281">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::scoring::components</title><para>Score-related ECS components.</para>
<para>This namespace contains components for associating entities with score pools, storing score values, and observing score changes.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_2e322012c304bd84ecea0543a8b62f92_1autotoc_md282">
<title>Components</title><para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
