</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Description  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>ScorePoolComponent</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Associates an entity with a score pool (e.g., player â†’ player&apos;s pool)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>ScoreValueComponent&lt;T&gt;</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Template component storing a score value of type T (e.g., KillReward)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>ScoreObserverComponent</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Observes a score pool and caches its value for UI display  </para>
